{"tid":2200571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西書：You better double me！占士笑而不語","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T10:42:04.000Z","uid":173952,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"97a9f9e6d4f86c033513ba726c6cf0aaa1d85007","tid":2200571,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"之後，韋斯卜克又和朗度發生口角，而且他對朗度和占士說：&ldquo;你們最好包夾我（You better double me！）&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  尷尬的是，此時湖人的領先優勢已經達到29分，聽到韋斯卜克的狂言之後，占士笑而不語。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vjLuuO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvjLuuO6.jpg&h=9b4a2c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  全場比賽，韋斯卜克13投僅4中，三分球3投0中，得到10分、4個籃板和6次助攻。<br />\n<br />\n  值得一提的是，韋斯卜克未來三年的平均薪水達到4380萬美元，但是他已經過了運動能力巔峰期。如今，韋斯卜克的投籃缺陷被無限放大，在半場陣地進攻中，湖人隊甚至都懶得去防守韋斯卜克的投籃。"},{"pid":"84e2278d5a67e893d1e6dbc5a50b992bde51ec71","tid":2200571,"uid":78574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:19:25.000Z","msg":"隊友駛撚mark咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85bb5316a16a7ddb0805ed77f28a86a39a8b211","tid":2200571,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U9636ET0guE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU9636ET0guE&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513W9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=ea6e889d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U9636ET0guE</a>"},{"pid":"681d8f05b14a5c41ab1b03a3816b497192d2e7e0","tid":2200571,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84e2278d5a67e893d1e6dbc5a50b992bde51ec71","tid":2200571,"uid":78574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:19:25.000Z","msg":"隊友駛撚mark咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"韋斯卜克未來三年的平均薪水達到4380萬美元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore